    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generic term used for various acid-free,100% cotton papers that are either of the Arches brand name or similar to those made under registered brand Arches. Although "Arches" is a registered trademark, the term has become generic through common usage. To indicate genuine paper of this band, prefer "Arches paper (R)."</Note_Text>
